video.title: Chrome Dev Tools: Audits Tab
video.description:
Info and mini-lesson on the 'Audits' tab of Chrome Dev Tools.

In this video, we do an audit of one of my Ziplines for Free Code Camp. 

The Audit tool walks you through how to improve your page step by step. 

That being said, none of these suggestions are required, but they definitely should be taken into consideration.
